p-level test class public in the earlier iteration: `public class Quarkus_test_commonTest`.\\n- [x] Added helper test implementations in the earlier iteration:\\n  - `SimpleConfig`\\n  - `StatefulTestResource`\\n  - `OrderedResource`\\n  - test consumer/context helper classes\\n  - annotation fixture types for `AnnotationUtils`\\n- [x] Initially used `MapConfigSource`, `SmallRyeConfig`, `SmallRyeConfigBuilder`, and `SimpleValueRegistry`; later removed them.\\n- [x] Replaced `SmallRyeConfigBuilder` / `SmallRyeConfig` with lightweight local `SimpleConfig implements Config`.\\n- [x] Replaced `ListeningAddress` registry/config test with `listeningAddressExposesProtocolAndPort`, covering `port()`, `protocol()`, and `isSsl()`.\\n- [x] External native-image failures were observed for logging/image-heap initialization:\\n  - `An object of type 'org.jboss.logmanager.Level' was found in the image heap.`\\n  - `An object of type 'org.jboss.logmanager.LogManager' was found in the image heap.`\\n  - `An object of type 'io.quarkus.bootstrap.logging.QuarkusDelayedHandler' was found in the image heap.`\\n- [x] Earlier build arg additions attempted:\\n  - `--initialize-at-build-time=org.jboss.logmanager.Level`\\n  - `--initialize-at-build-time=org.jboss.logmanager.LogManager,org.jboss.logmanager.Level`\\n  - `--initialize-at-build-time=org.jboss.logmanager.LogManager,org.jboss.logmanager.Level,io.quarkus.bootstrap.logging.QuarkusDelayedHandler`\\n- [x] A later external run failed with additional logging image-heap errors:\\n  - `An object of type 'org.jboss.logmanager.AtomicArray' was found in the image heap.`\\n  - `An object of type 'org.jboss.logmanager.errormanager.OnlyOnceErrorManager' was found in the image heap.`\\n  - Both were reached via `org.jboss.logmanager.ExtHandler.<init>(ExtHandler.java:79/80/82)`.\\n- [x] Temporarily broadened the native init build arg in `tests/src/io.quarkus/quarkus-test-common/3.33.1/build.gradle`:\\n  - from `--initialize-at-build-time=org.jboss